dct_title_s: Plan of the Borough of Island Heights, Ocean County, New Jersey
dct_description_sm: This map is a plan of Island Heights showing property lots. The blocks and individual lots are numbered and the streets surrounding them are labelled. It also gives information on the width of the streets and the sidewalks.
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
